<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Modal Window</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        
        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); 
            z-index: 10;
        }

    
        .modal {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%); 
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 400px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            z-index: 20;
        }

        .modal h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>What is Lorem Ipsum?</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. ... (багато тексту для фону)</p>

    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="modal">
        <h2>MODAL WINDOW</h2>
        <p>Mauris tristique sagittis tincidunt. Maecenas congue nisi porttitor volutpat mattis. Aliquam nec lorem mi. Suspendisse ornare, neque eget maximus cursus, augue diam convallis felis, at condimentum quam orci id diam.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
